  <title>Environmental Sustainability in WASH package</title>
  <description rain:type="d_duration_months" type="3">16</description>
  <description akvo:type="8" rain:type="d_objectives" type="2">A better understanding of the role and importance of Environmental Sustainability in the set up of new water (related) projects.</description>
  <description akvo:type="4" rain:type="subtitle" type="1">Communication package for promotion and knowledge sharing</description>
