  <description akvo:type="5" rain:type="d_summary" type="1">The overall goal of this project is to motivate Dutch WASH Alliance members to include sustainability into the set-up of new water related projects through visualizing the concept of E-sustainabiity. As spin off, communication about this approach should lead to incorporation of E-sustainability in projects of non Dutch WASH Alliance members.</description>
  <description rain:description="General (short) project description" rain:type="description" type="3">The project consists of the development of 4 factsheets in English and French on Environmental Sustainability and the production of a short animation.</description>
